6-column kicker coupled with a 6-column, 2-line hedline on the
House impeachment vote.
</P>
<P>
   For early editions, The Times plans 4 pages of stories and 4
pages of text from wire services. The coverage will expand
following completion of voting in the House. We will update
advisories as needed.
</P>
