   Ray Blake OL 6-3 270 Hinesville (Bradwell Inst.)
</P>
<P>
   Winfred Brown CB 5-10 170 Kennesaw (Harrison)
</P>
<P>
   Brian Camp QB 6-2 225 Dublin, OH (Coffman)
</P>
