president of the 20th century to be impeached by the House,
President Clinton launched a fight to save his administration. In a
statement read at the White House while surrounded by his
Democratic supporters, Clinton was expected to ask the country to
put his misconduct behind it and mend the tears a year of scandal
and partisanship has ripped in the national fabric. (Deans, Cox
News Service) WITH PHOTOS
