books. It was supreme drama supercharged by shocking news. As if
impeaching a president were not awe-inspiring enough, the House on
Saturday presented the additional spectacles of a speaker-elect
resigning over past adultery, a mass Democratic walkout from the
chamber, and the president's wife making an emotional plea for his
political survival. (Dart, Cox News Service) WITH PHOTOS. MOVED
